1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 17=

4
00:00:20,679 --> 00:00:21,239
Grandfather!

5
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:26,160
Easy, my boy. Why are you panicking?

6
00:00:26,679 --> 00:00:28,800
How many times have I told you?

7
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:31,000
You're the heir of Tang Clan.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:33,079
Whatever happens, you must stay calm.

9
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:34,439
Take your time.

10
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,200
Peng Dasheng...

11
00:00:35,439 --> 00:00:36,479
He's gone.

12
00:00:36,679 --> 00:00:37,640
What?

13
00:00:42,719 --> 00:00:43,520
Master.

14
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,759
I've decided not to return to the sect.

15
00:00:47,039 --> 00:00:47,719
Wait.

16
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,840
Why?

17
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,439
A man lives but once,

18
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,240
and grass but one season.

19
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:55,840
If I can't live true to myself,

20
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,759
what good is immortality?

21
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,000
Dasheng,

22
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,439
you need to think this through.

23
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:07,400
You're fated to die
on your twentieth birthday.

24
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,760
No one can change that.

25
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,959
No matter what you do

26
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:13,079
or how you do it,

27
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:15,840
you can't escape that fate.

28
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:17,319
Master,

29
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:20,239
I've made my choice.

30
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:23,500
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

31
00:01:23,740 --> 00:01:27,220
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

32
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:28,940
♪I rise against fate and fight♪
(Huxiao Manor)

33
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:30,780
(Huxiao Manor)

34
00:01:30,780 --> 00:01:33,060
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

35
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:36,220
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

36
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:38,959
- Move!
- Hurry!

37
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:41,740
(Memorial Tablet)

38
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,359
Peng Dasheng?

39
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,079
You...

40
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:57,040
The trap at Taiping Villa...

41
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:59,120
You sent me there
on purpose, didn't you?

42
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:01,400
You wanted the Demon Sect to kill me

43
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,840
so you could keep your hands clean.

44
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:05,000
You're quite the schemer.

45
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,639
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

46
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,039
Really?

47
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,439
Maybe you'll understand
what he has to say.

48
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:13,840
Ms. Duan!

49
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:18,879
I...

50
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:20,159
Wangcai!

51
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:23,759
Tell him exactly
what you told us just now.

52
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,360
That day... it was Mr. Lin...

53
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,680
Mr. Lin told me to trick Mr. Peng

54
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,960
into going to Taiping Villa
to visit a patient.

55
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:31,879
Afterward, he sent men to silence me.

56
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,080
If these two ladies
hadn't arrived in time,

57
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,960
my family and I would already be dead.

58
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,680
That... that's a vicious lie!

59
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,479
Lin Dun!

60
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,879
My biggest regret

61
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:45,840
is letting you live that day.

62
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,039
That's why I'm here

63
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:53,039
to kill you myself.

64
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,960
Whoever kills him for me

65
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,800
gets ten thousand in silver!

66
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:02,680
Go! What are you waiting for?

67
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,680
Get him! All of you!

68
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:06,680
I've got money! Protect me!

69
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,080
Back off if you don't want to die.

70
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,280
Get him!

71
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,400
Protect me!

72
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:23,000
I'm sorry, Mr. Peng.

73
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,759
Please don't kill me.

74
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:27,080
I'll give you everything
the Lin family owns.

75
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,960
Land, treasures,

76
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,680
and even Huxiao Manor.

77
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,560
It's all yours.

78
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,360
Please, just don't kill me.

79
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,479
And Xiaojiu's life?

80
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,319
How will you repay that?

81
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,800
No.

82
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,360
It wasn't me.

83
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,080
It was...

84
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:50,400
Song Qingbo of the Yizihuijian Sect.

85
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,680
He made me do it.

86
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,639
He said if I helped him,

87
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:56,120
he'd restore Huxiao Manor to glory.

88
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,280
Why should I believe you?

89
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,680
Wangcai received Song Qingbo

90
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,240
at the gate that day.

91
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:05,360
Say something!

92
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,280
See? I wasn't lying.

93
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:13,639
(So someone else was behind
Xiaojiu's death.)

94
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:19,079
Mr. Peng, you'll spare me?

95
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:22,279
(Song Qingbo!)

96
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,560
Thank you, Mr. Peng.

97
00:04:35,879 --> 00:04:37,360
You got Xiaojiu killed.

98
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,959
Why would I spare you?

99
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:51,160
I know I deserve to die.

100
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:54,000
I only ask that you spare my family.

101
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:57,399
Don't worry. I won't hurt them.

102
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,360
Thank you, Mr. Peng.

103
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,079
You were forced into it

104
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,399
because they threatened your family.

105
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,480
I won't kill you.

106
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,600
Go.

107
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,680
Mr. Peng!

108
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:26,079
Please take me as your disciple.

109
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:28,160
Why?

110
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:31,160
I've worked for the Lin family
since I was a child, for over ten years.

111
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,240
They treated me like an animal,

112
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,959
and I never complained.

113
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,040
But when they put a blade

114
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,199
to my sister's throat,

115
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,079
I finally realized

116
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,959
that without any real skill,

117
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:42,279
I can't even protect my own family.

118
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:44,079
I want to learn martial arts from you.

119
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,879
I don't care about fame.

120
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,439
I just want to keep my family safe.

121
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,560
(The night the Demon Sect
attacked my home,)

122
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:53,959
(Father and Mother
fought to the death to protect me.)

123
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,680
(But I couldn't even protect myself.)

124
00:05:57,839 --> 00:05:59,000
(I often wonder)

125
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,519
(if I had your strength,)

126
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:04,759
(would Father and Mother
still be alive?)

127
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,279
Get up.

128
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:21,720
You...

129
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,480
You'll take me as your disciple?

130
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,360
What's your name?

131
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,839
My surname is Zhang.

132
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:28,959
We were poor, so I had no given name.

133
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,759
Mr. Lin always called me Wangcai,

134
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:32,600
so that's what I became known as.

135
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:38,000
My master once told me,
"Free of worry, free of fear."

136
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:41,399
From now on, you'll be called Wuji,
"the Fearless."

137
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:42,800
Thank you for naming me, Master.

138
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,399
And remember this.

139
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:47,000
Don't drop to your knees
before everyone you meet.

140
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,639
In this world,

141
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,040
no one but Heaven, Earth,
and your parents

142
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:51,920
is worth kneeling to.

143
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:53,959
Yes, Master. I'll remember.

144
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:27,959
Changsheng,

145
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:29,600
you're getting better and better

146
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,800
with the Guigu Divine Needles.

147
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,319
Master,

148
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:34,839
please stop praising me.

149
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,439
The spiritual power inside you

150
00:07:36,439 --> 00:07:38,600
may be raising your cultivation,

151
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:40,360
but it's also burning through

152
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:43,040
what little life force you have left.

153
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,120
If you keep using it

154
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,399
so recklessly...

155
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:46,639
I...

156
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:50,319
Once it reaches your heart meridian,

157
00:07:50,319 --> 00:07:52,800
not even an immortal

158
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,920
could save you.

159
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,319
(When I was little,)

160
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,920
(while my senior brothers
trained outside,)

161
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:04,759
(Master made me stay in and study.)

162
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:07,040
(He worried the sun would burn me)

163
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,040
(and the cold wind would chill me.)

164
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:11,639
(I was like a sheltered orchid)

165
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:12,600
(that was never allowed to grow.)

166
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,160
(But Master never knew)

167
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:18,120
(I'd rather be a weed growing wild.)

168
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,240
An orchid in a hidden valley

169
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,720
still finds its own path to the sky.

170
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:38,759
He got what he wanted after all.

171
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,200
Master.

172
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,919
Are you really
not going back to the sect?

173
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:53,240
I've decided to stay

174
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,720
and avenge Xiaojiu.

175
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:58,120
Is this all for her?

176
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,240
Not entirely.

177
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:01,919
Before I left the sect,

178
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,919
I was like a caged animal.

179
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:06,240
The fence Master
built around me was my whole world.

180
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:08,159
But after Xiaojiu died,

181
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,000
I realized

182
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,000
that I don't want to drift through life.

183
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:14,440
We only live once.

184
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,840
Instead of always holding back,

185
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,919
I'd rather give it everything I've got.

186
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:21,440
But Master, the Demon Sect
is powerful and deeply entrenched.

187
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,840
And the Luocha Blade Demon

188
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,919
is beyond the second rank.

189
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,320
That spiritual power
may make you stronger,

190
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,360
but you're paying for it with your life.

191
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,360
What chance do you have?

192
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,840
Whether I can beat him or not,

193
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:37,039
I'm fighting.

194
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:40,399
Even with only a ten percent chance,

195
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,799
I'll risk my life.

196
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:43,679
All right.

197
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,360
Since you've made up your mind,

198
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:49,360
I'm no coward either.

199
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:51,360
I'll give you everything I've got.

200
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:54,840
Thanks, Changsheng.

201
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,320
We have a lead on Song Qingbo.

202
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,960
Murong Xiang is holding
a Martial Arts Assembly today.

203
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:01,480
Song Qingbo was invited.

204
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,279
Song Qingbo!

205
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:04,840
Master, wait.

206
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:06,799
Hear Ms. Duan out.

207
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,320
The assembly will be packed
with top martial artists.

208
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,799
They won't let a junior cause trouble.

209
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,039
Without solid proof,

210
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,639
how can you bring
Song Qingbo to justice?

211
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:16,519
Master, Ms. Duan has a point.

212
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,919
Song Qingbo has grown
much stronger over the years.

213
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:20,720
Especially, his Zhougong Sword Art

214
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,639
has nearly reached the Perfection Realm.

215
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,360
The spiritual power inside you

216
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,200
has boosted your cultivation,

217
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:29,600
but your meridians can't take much more.

218
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:30,840
If it goes out of control,

219
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,840
it could kill you.

220
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,039
He colluded with the Demon Sect

221
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:36,039
and got Xiaojiu killed.

222
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,639
Even if it's a death trap,

223
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:40,240
I'm going in.

224
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,240
Then,

225
00:10:42,519 --> 00:10:43,440
count me in.

226
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,720
I have my own score
to settle with the Demon Sect.

227
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,960
Whatever this brings, I'm with you.

228
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:55,320
Master Baiyi of the Demon Sect
has issued a challenge at Liuchu Manor.

229
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:58,919
His sinister ambitions
are plain for all to see.

230
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:01,200
My daughter was taken by the Demon Sect

231
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,919
and nearly killed.

232
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,159
That is why I've gathered you here

233
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,440
to form an alliance
against the Demon Sect

234
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,320
and choose a commander

235
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,039
to lead us.

236
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:15,039
Amitabha.

237
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:18,000
More than thirty monks
from our Shaolin branch temple

238
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,879
were slaughtered in a single night.

239
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:24,200
We will avenge them!

240
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,240
Avenge them!

241
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,320
Avenge them!

242
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,200
Avenge them!

243
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,840
A disciple of our Kongtong Sect

244
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,559
was taken by the Demon Sect
and used to test their drugs.

245
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:34,919
By the time we found him,
nothing remained but bones.

246
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,600
An atrocity!

247
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:40,399
I ask you all to join us
in destroying these monsters.

248
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,799
Destroy these monsters!

249
00:11:41,919 --> 00:11:43,000
Destroy these monsters!

250
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,200
Destroy these monsters!

251
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,440
Destroy these monsters!

252
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,960
Destroy these monsters!

253
00:11:48,639 --> 00:11:49,559
Master Murong,

254
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:52,840
I am Song Qingbo,
leader of the Yizihuijian Sect.

255
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,759
I volunteer to command the alliance

256
00:11:54,759 --> 00:11:57,000
and lead our forces
in destroying the Demon Sect.

257
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,399
I object.

258
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:12,639
Is that

259
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:16,080
Mr. Peng, the one who defeated

260
00:12:16,159 --> 00:12:17,399
the Northern Evil Duo and their master?

261
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,840
Mr. Song,

262
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:29,840
surprised I'm still alive?

263
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,639
Mr. Peng,

264
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:35,559
I don't know what you mean.

265
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:39,240
Then let me spell it out for you.

266
00:12:40,039 --> 00:12:43,039
Song Qingbo colluded
with the Demon Sect.

267
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,960
He set a trap for me at Taiping Villa

268
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,639
and tried to kill me.

269
00:12:48,039 --> 00:12:49,600
Now he wants

270
00:12:49,639 --> 00:12:51,840
to command the alliance against them.

271
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:53,440
Don't you find that

272
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,039
shameless and ridiculous?

273
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,320
Fellow martial artists,

274
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:59,240
only sect leaders

275
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:01,639
may attend today's assembly.

276
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:04,200
This arrogant nobody
has no title or standing.

277
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:07,320
He should be removed at once.

278
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:08,519
Mr. Song,

279
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,440
Dasheng hasn't even finished,

280
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,639
and you're already
trying to throw him out.

281
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:14,799
Feeling guilty?

282
00:13:14,799 --> 00:13:15,200
You...

283
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:16,759
Song Qingbo,

284
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:21,840
is Peng Dasheng telling the truth?

285
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,200
Master Murong,

286
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,519
I swear to Heaven.

287
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:27,440
If any of that is true,

288
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,639
may lightning strike me dead.

289
00:13:29,039 --> 00:13:31,240
Amitabha.

290
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,399
Mr. Peng,

291
00:13:32,679 --> 00:13:37,039
do you have any proof?

292
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:41,759
My proof is on the way.

293
00:13:44,639 --> 00:13:46,919
What a ridiculous accusation!

294
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:51,720
You dare falsely accuse
a sect leader without proof?

295
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,960
Master Murong,

296
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:57,600
under the rules of the martial world,
what punishment does one face

297
00:13:57,600 --> 00:14:00,440
for making a baseless accusation
against a fellow martial artist?

298
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,440
Anyone who accuses a sect leader
without proof must face

299
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,919
the Three Trials to prove
he's telling the truth.

300
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,799
The Three Trials?

301
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:09,720
- What?
- The Three Trials?

302
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:14,360
What are the Three Trials?

303
00:14:14,639 --> 00:14:16,639
(The Three Trials require)

304
00:14:16,639 --> 00:14:18,720
(the accuser to take
three palm strikes barehanded.)

305
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:19,879
(The three strikes are called)

306
00:14:19,879 --> 00:14:21,720
(Test of Courage, Clarity of Heart,
and Attainment of the Way.)

307
00:14:21,919 --> 00:14:23,919
(If the accuser
withstands all three strikes,)

308
00:14:23,919 --> 00:14:26,000
(the matter ends there.)

309
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,279
(If he fails,)

310
00:14:27,279 --> 00:14:29,919
(the striker bears no responsibility.)

311
00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:31,919
Fellow martial artists,

312
00:14:31,919 --> 00:14:33,519
every senior figure

313
00:14:33,759 --> 00:14:35,639
is here today.

314
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,440
You can all bear witness.

315
00:14:38,159 --> 00:14:39,240
Peng Dasheng,

316
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:42,039
do you dare take three strikes from me?

317
00:14:43,519 --> 00:14:45,320
Why are you so eager, Mr. Song?

318
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,000
Trying to silence me for good?

319
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:47,519
You...

320
00:14:47,759 --> 00:14:49,000
What nonsense!

321
00:14:50,679 --> 00:14:54,200
If I agree to take the three strikes,

322
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:57,600
will everyone hear me out afterward?

323
00:14:58,039 --> 00:15:01,440
We will investigate
the matter thoroughly

324
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,200
and see that justice is done.

325
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:04,960
All right.

326
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:08,519
Then I, Peng Dasheng,
will face the Three Trials

327
00:15:08,639 --> 00:15:09,840
and prove I'm telling the truth.

328
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,120
Wait.

329
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:13,639
Amitabha.

330
00:15:13,639 --> 00:15:16,559
Mr. Peng, think carefully.

331
00:15:16,559 --> 00:15:18,960
The Three Trials are no small matter.

332
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,559
Everyone who's faced them

333
00:15:20,559 --> 00:15:22,159
has been killed or badly injured.

334
00:15:22,159 --> 00:15:24,399
No one has ever walked away unscathed.

335
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,840
Be warned.

336
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:27,480
Those three strikes

337
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:30,279
could cost you your life.

338
00:15:30,919 --> 00:15:32,240
Thank you for your concern.

339
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,720
My mind is made up.

340
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,399
Then so be it.

341
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:40,399
Mr. Peng, you may begin
the Three Trials.

342
00:15:53,420 --> 00:15:53,900
♪Come on♪

343
00:15:57,420 --> 00:15:59,100
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

344
00:16:01,060 --> 00:16:04,020
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

345
00:16:04,300 --> 00:16:07,220
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

346
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:10,300
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

347
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:13,300
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

348
00:16:13,820 --> 00:16:16,780
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

349
00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:20,020
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

350
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:23,100
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

351
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:26,020
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

352
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:29,900
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

353
00:16:29,940 --> 00:16:32,940
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

354
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:38,620
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

355
00:16:39,020 --> 00:16:41,060
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

356
00:16:41,620 --> 00:16:44,140
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

357
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:47,260
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

358
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:51,060
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

359
00:16:51,660 --> 00:16:53,780
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

360
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:56,820
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

361
00:16:56,980 --> 00:17:00,260
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

362
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:04,580
♪I am my own king♪

363
00:17:17,660 --> 00:17:19,220
♪I emerge into the world♪

364
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:20,980
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

365
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:22,340
♪My pride is my trump card♪

366
00:17:22,340 --> 00:17:24,140
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

367
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:25,540
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

368
00:17:25,540 --> 00:17:27,300
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

369
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:28,820
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

370
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:30,540
♪I dare to break every rule♪

371
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:31,860
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

372
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:33,700
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

373
00:17:33,700 --> 00:17:34,940
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

374
00:17:34,940 --> 00:17:37,180
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

375
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:38,700
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

376
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:40,300
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

377
00:17:40,300 --> 00:17:41,900
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

378
00:17:41,900 --> 00:17:43,620
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

379
00:17:43,620 --> 00:17:45,340
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

380
00:17:45,340 --> 00:17:46,700
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

381
00:17:46,700 --> 00:17:48,340
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

382
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:49,820
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

383
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:51,540
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

384
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:53,140
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

385
00:17:53,140 --> 00:17:54,700
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

386
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:59,020
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

387
00:17:59,020 --> 00:18:01,180
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

388
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:03,780
♪Let me write the legend♪

389
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:11,220
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

390
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:14,540
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

391
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:17,020
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

392
00:18:17,020 --> 00:18:21,100
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

393
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:24,060
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

394
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:26,540
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

395
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:29,580
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

396
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:34,620
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
